   <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:links" underlined="true">creative mode</style>
   does not consume durability when used). A wrench with a durability of 0 will be destroyed directly after being used again. A wrench with less than full durability can be used at
   <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:links" underlined="true">
 Tantalum - Tantalum
